DESCRIPTION:Room 6\\\, Blue Building \\nResilient neighborhoods start with 
	strong connections. When we work together\\\, we’re better prepared to bou
	nce back from any disaster. Whether you live in a house\\\, apartment\\\, 
	or condo\\\, learn how to team up with your neighbors to stay safe. \\nPhi
	nney Hub makes it easy (and fun!) to get your block organized. We provide 
	the tools and support you need to turn preparedness into a great way to me
	et neighbors. Come see how simple it is to build a safer\\\, more connecte
	d community together. \\nPresented by Phinney Emergency Hub \\nQuestions? 
	Please email: PhinneyHub@gmail.com \\n  \\n\n\nhttps://www.phinneycenter.o
	rg/event/phinney-neighbors-organize-neighborhood-preparedness-orientation/
